</node>
<node id="DIVIDEND DISTRIBUTION EVENT">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">In January 2021, Acme Government Solutions made a significant decision to distribute $5 million of dividends to its shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;In June 2019, InnovateTech distributed $10 million in dividends to shareholders, enhancing shareholder returns.&lt;SEP&gt;Occurred in November 2019, distributing $1 million to shareholders, enhancing shareholder returns.</data>
