<node id="GOVERNMENT CONTRACT ACQUISITION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Acme Government Solutions acquired a major government contract worth $100 million, driving operating income and profitability.&lt;SEP&gt;Entertainment Enterprises Inc. successfully acquired a major government contract, contributing to the increase in total assets.&lt;SEP&gt;The successful acquisition of a major government contract worth $100 million in March 2021.</data>
