<node id="COMPLIANCE AND REGULATORY UPDATES">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">In November 2017, SkyQuest Airlines proactively monitored and implemented compliance updates to manage and mitigate risks associated with regulatory changes, ensuring adherence to industry standards.&lt;SEP&gt;Occurred in March 2021, ensuring adherence to laws and regulations for ethical practices and transparency.&lt;SEP&gt;Updates were implemented in February 2021 to ensure adherence to laws and regulations, reducing legal risk and protecting shareholder interests.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b2fe366c1e03267f881e81f6b3c08b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d84e126fbb147f6630018352a054dde3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a70da148e47a53e6b867701402bc57b</data>
