<node id="BOARD OF DIRECTORS CHANGE">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Appointment of new members to Acme's board in April 2020 for fresh perspectives and expertise.&lt;SEP&gt;In April 2017, SkyQuest Airlines experienced a change in its Board of Directors with the appointment of a respected industry leader as Chairman, expected to impact strategic direction and shareholder interests.&lt;SEP&gt;In April 2021, new board members brought diverse expertise impacting strategic direction and governance.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b2fe366c1e03267f881e81f6b3c08b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a70da148e47a53e6b867701402bc57b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bb6a190ca92adef85bc4837417841ea</data>
