  <data key="d1">Changes in senior management positions, including CEO, occurred in November 2021, potentially leading to adjustments in operational focus and strategic priorities.&lt;SEP&gt;In May 2021, senior management changes aligned the team with corporate vision and goals.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b2fe366c1e03267f881e81f6b3c08b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d84e126fbb147f6630018352a054dde3</data>
