  <data key="d2">chunk-aca93e51cb89abee49a4c47d5b74548a</data>
</node>
<node id="$50 MILLION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Amount distributed in dividends to shareholders in January 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividend distributed to shareholders in July 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;InnovaTech generated a cash flow of $50 million in 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;JetWing Aviation's net profit was $50 million, showcasing the company's ability to generate earnings.&lt;SEP&gt;The acquisition cost of MedTech Innovations by HealthLife Solutions in September 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed to shareholders by Acme Financial Services in February 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount raised through equity and debt financing to strengthen operations expansion and accelerate new technology development.&lt;SEP&gt;The major investment made by Entertainment Enterprises Inc. for film production in March 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;The net profit increased to $50 million due to the strategic partnership with a major technology company in April 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The total change in cash for EduCorp was reflected by its cash flow of $50 million.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f140b4d480a658bee39d8a4c621c4fab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0d51014d28425d87ceb8e2b84393395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a59a1aa9be0dda8d445a8324bb60018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a13a1ab41c0cd055a4aea8f61c29426&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ae9afa65ef8f71c3dd7c7c926bf42f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d343d9b6488370b6fbfb6dea6a2c35b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aca93e51cb89abee49a4c47d5b74548a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f669e0066e8cbea19e1648059317fea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f48527548a1038a9e631dfd29d258ea1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373cea03acf2045695d804e957ea60de</data>
