<node id="$300 MILLION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt reduced by SkyQuest Airlines through debt restructuring in June, improving the company's financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Projected global box office revenue from the blockbuster film "The Great Escape" acquired in March 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;Shareholder equity amounted to $300 million, representing the equity belonging to shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Shareholder equity of HealthLife Solutions at the end of the accounting period in 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The reported total liabilities reflect the total amount of debts owed by the company at the end of the accounting period.&lt;SEP&gt;The total amount of equity owned by shareholders for EduCorp was $300 million.</data>
