  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">In December 2021, Fabrikon undertook debt restructuring, reducing liabilities by $20 million and improving its overall financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;In July 2019, Entertainment Enterprises Inc. completed debt restructuring to optimize capital structure and reduce liabilities by $20 million.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b2969dc24f3d6abff422d9110e0611b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aca93e51cb89abee49a4c47d5b74548a</data>
