<node id="$100 MILLION BOND ISSUANCE">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">In August 2019, Entertainment Enterprises Inc. raised $100 million through bond issuance to strengthen its financial position for expansion and development.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aca93e51cb89abee49a4c47d5b74548a</data>
</node>
<node id="ASSET RESTRUCTURING">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Actions taken by Retail Emporium to optimize capital operations and resource use.&lt;SEP&gt;An asset restructuring in March 2021 to optimize business structure and consolidate resources in key growth areas.&lt;SEP&gt;Consolidation of media production and distribution businesses for operational efficiency in December.&lt;SEP&gt;Efficiently streamlined operations and capital allocation.&lt;SEP&gt;In 2019, Energen Solutions Ltd consolidated its wind power division while divesting non-performing solar assets to improve operational efficiency and overall value.&lt;SEP&gt;In April 2021, GreenTech Solutions Inc. optimized its business structure to focus on high-growth sectors within environmental protection industry, improving operational efficiency and research capabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;In January 2019, InnovateTech implemented a comprehensive asset restructuring strategy to streamline operations and reduce costs, enhancing operational efficiency and overall value.&lt;SEP&gt;In January 2020, EduCorp underwent an asset restructuring to optimize its business structure and focus on core educational services.&lt;SEP&gt;In July, Energex underwent asset restructuring impacting shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;In November 2019, EcoGuard Solutions restructured its assets to optimize business operations and enhance efficiency.&lt;SEP&gt;In October 2019, the company underwent asset restructuring focusing on core entertainment businesses and divesting non-core assets for operational efficiency improvement.&lt;SEP&gt;Optimization of business structure to improve efficiency and value in May 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;The company also underwent asset restructuring in December 2018 leading to improved operational efficiency and increased value.&lt;SEP&gt;The company divested non-core assets to focus on healthcare technology solutions, enhancing operational efficiency and value.&lt;SEP&gt;Undertook asset restructuring in February to optimize business structure and improve operational efficiency.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9f71b88e6766340672e6b89412a8c73d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d244671976e2cae945d2423f0ea6c7e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78a33344b4fba4ba3bd201f84d0c42a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0d51014d28425d87ceb8e2b84393395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a13a1ab41c0cd055a4aea8f61c29426&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e03c76828847c0eff32de78f7b01fde6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78ab8d8648edc98c46e93bc046fafb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-975be914f8bb23cf2cc514afda9287d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4255846d834db8367922bc6ac062c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aca93e51cb89abee49a4c47d5b74548a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-977da11f80e6da998b8affc5dd2357b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd6d69cb677a9b4ebed6240eaab28fff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5bd42f2bd7e075097081591743844fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d73178a270a56ecd4b5a838ae17c9002&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d666eb7ec66a94b27cfcc56006ae5eab</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 41}]</data>
</node>
