<node id="DEBT RESTRUCTURING">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt restructuring can modify the terms and amounts owed on debts.&lt;SEP&gt;Debt restructuring reducing liabilities by $100 million in April 2017, improving financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;HealthLife Solutions reduced liabilities by $25 million through debt restructuring in June 2020, improving financial condition and reducing costs.&lt;SEP&gt;In 2018, Green Fields Agriculture Co underwent debt restructuring, which involved renegotiating terms with creditors to improve its financial health and operational flexibility.&lt;SEP&gt;In 2019, a debt restructuring event took place in January aimed at optimizing the company's capital structure and reducing liabilities by $25 million.&lt;SEP&gt;In December 2021, the company underwent debt restructuring reducing liabilities by $15 million and improving financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;In December, Energex underwent debt restructuring optimizing its debt obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2020, EduCorp underwent debt restructuring to reduce liabilities by $5 million.&lt;SEP&gt;In November 2018, Capital Finance Group underwent debt restructuring reducing liabilities by $100 million, improving financial condition and reducing costs.&lt;SEP&gt;In September 2019, EcoGuard Solutions underwent debt restructuring, reducing its liabilities by $15 million and improving financial stability.&lt;SEP&gt;Occurred in October 2021, reducing liabilities by $20 million and improving financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Performed by Culture Innovators Ltd. in July 2021, resulting in a reduction of liabilities by $15 million.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced liabilities by $15 million through debt restructuring in December, improving financial condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced liabilities by $20 million to improve financial stability.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced liabilities by $5 million through refinancing at lower interest rates.&lt;SEP&gt;Revising terms of existing debt agreements for improved financial stability.&lt;SEP&gt;SkyQuest Airlines underwent debt restructuring reducing its liabilities by $300 million.&lt;SEP&gt;This event reduced liabilities by $15 million, enhancing financial condition and profitability while lowering associated costs.</data>
