<node id="ETHICS AND INTEGRITY INCIDENT">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A former employee found guilty of fraud and corruption, tarnishing the company's reputation and brand value.&lt;SEP&gt;A key incident that impacted HealthLife Solutions' reputation in January 2020, raising concerns about ethical conduct and transparency.&lt;SEP&gt;An employee fraud case led to a significant ethics and integrity incident for Sunrise Holidays in January 2019, necessitating immediate action to address the issue and prevent future occurrences.&lt;SEP&gt;Faced an incident involving conflicts of interest and took measures to address it in October 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;In April 2020, an ethics and integrity incident related to conflicts of interest occurred, leading to disciplinary actions and reinforcing the company's commitment to transparency and accountability.&lt;SEP&gt;In August 2017, Evergreen promptly addressed a minor ethics and integrity incident related to an employee violation of the internal code of conduct. The company conducted a thorough investigation, terminated the employee, and reinforced ethics training across all departments.&lt;SEP&gt;In August 2019, EcoGuard Solutions took prompt measures to investigate an incident of unauthorized data access and enhanced its cybersecurity measures and provided employee training.&lt;SEP&gt;Significant ethics and integrity incident uncovered within Acme Financial Services in February 2020, leading to tarnished reputation and decline in brand value.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d1fbac375634b3f01f8f3469051ba632&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b650f32e9ea4fa3555f038c2b4cc5fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-672984301753d0e346cd1c5cc1cfe908&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bedf5ae312b9a8bac4ad0966c12a3105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afc39062474c2158f187bbc11faf781a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bb6a190ca92adef85bc4837417841ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1eb48c0373aea3220ecac2a958a1fdc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-830a569fd6d01d8b1e34d9f714515d8a</data>
